 OF MICROFORMS IN CARIBBEAN LIBRARIES: A REPORT TO THE ACURIL MICROFILMCOMMITTEE 1978 SURVEY SUBMITTED TO ACURIL STANDING COMMITTEE ON MICROFILM,NOVEMBER 5-10, 1978, BARBADOS.A SURVEY QUESTIONNAIRE WAS SENT TO ALL 81 MEMBER INSTITUTIONS OF ACURIL(ASSOCIATION OF CARIBBEAN UNIVERSITY RESEARCH AND INSTITUTIONAL LIBRARIES) TODETERMINE THEIR MICROFORM HOLDINGS AND EQUIPMENT. DATA IS TABULATED, WITHANALYSIS. MANY COLLECTIONS ARE SMALL BUT CAN BE EXPECTED TO GROW, AND OVER 1/3OF RESPONDENTS OFFER MICROFORMS ON INTERLIBRARY LOAN